OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778193330
OL,3,CManuscripts and photographs belonging
OL,4,Cto Thomas Hardy made accessible to
OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,FAn archive of materials belonging to
OL,8,Fauthor Thomas Hardy have been made
OL,9,Faccessible to the public.
OL,11,FHardy was born in Dorset in 1840 and
OL,12,Flived in the county for most of his
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FItems including manuscripts for three
OL,16,Fof his major novels, his notebooks,
OL,17,Fphotographs and more than 5,000
OL,18,Fletters are free to access at the
OL,19,FDorset History Centre in Dorchester.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
