PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778193330
OL,3,CManuscripts and photographs belonging
OL,4,Cto Thomas Hardy made accessible to
OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,FThe catalogue can also be viewed
OL,8,Fonline.
OL,10,FDorset Council said it is the largest
OL,11,Fcollection of Hardy material in the
OL,12,Fworld and highlights many aspects of
OL,13,Fhis life including his youth and early
OL,14,Fcareer as an architect.
OL,16,FIt includes school exercise books,
OL,17,Farchitectural drawings, sketches, and
OL,18,Fthe Hardy family music books.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
