OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778193330
OL,3,CManuscripts and photographs belonging
OL,4,Cto Thomas Hardy made accessible to
OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,FCouncillor Ryan Hope, Dorset Council's
OL,8,FCabinet Member for Customer, Culture
OL,9,Fand Community Engagement, said: "It is
OL,10,Fa privilege for the county to hold an
OL,11,Farchive of such scale and importance.
OL,13,F"This remarkable collection shows how
OL,14,Fdeeply Dorset shaped Hardy's
OL,15,Fimagination, and we know it will
OL,16,Finspire new generations of readers and
OL,17,Fresearchers to engage with some of the
OL,18,Fcounty's most significant cultural
OL,19,Fheritage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
