PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778193330
OL,3,CManuscripts and photographs belonging
OL,4,Cto Thomas Hardy made accessible to
OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,F"A huge thank you to everyone who
OL,8,Fdonated to make this project possible,
OL,9,Fthe History Centre for their
OL,10,Fdiligence, patience and never-ending
OL,11,Fenthusiasm and all those organisations
OL,12,Fand supporters of Hardy who continue
OL,13,Fto bring him to the attention of new
OL,14,Fgenerations of readers."
OL,16,FEleven notebooks filled with Hardy's
OL,17,Fhandwriting have been digitised and
OL,18,Fare free to view online, along with
OL,19,Fdraft manuscripts of Under the
OL,20,FGreenwood Tree, The Mayor of
OL,21,FCasterbridge and The Woodlanders.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
