PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778193330
OL,3,CManuscripts and photographs belonging
OL,4,Cto Thomas Hardy made accessible to
OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,FThomas Hardy gifted his manuscript of
OL,8,FThe Mayor of Casterbridge to Dorset
OL,9,FCounty Museum in 1911, marking the
OL,10,Fbeginning of the archive.
OL,12,FMark Chutter, Chair and Academic
OL,13,FDirector of the Thomas Hardy Society,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The collection is fascinating,
OL,15,Fintriguing and highly eclectic."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
